title: ETH v1 Update: Raise $AXS collateral cap
body:
Intro: This is a vote to raise the collateral cap of AXS on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market.

Proposal: Listing Committee

Rational: AXS is currently capped out on the ETH v1 market.

For:
Raise collateral cap of $AXS to 18,224 or $1.25M USD.

Against:
Do not make any changes to the ETH v1 market.
author: 0x6B1050C1C6B288C79Ac1db299Dc481048aBBBbcD
